# Windows-Sandbox install harness (#76). temp.env holds a REAL throwaway API key
# and each run writes an out-<timestamp>/ folder -- neither is caught by the plain
# `.env` / `*.log` rules above, so pin them here (a stray `git add -A` must never
# stage the key). setup.ps1 / setup.bat below are throwaway copies for a `local`
# run (see sandbox/README.md); the canonical ones live in the repo root.
sandbox/temp.env
sandbox/out-*/
sandbox/setup.ps1
sandbox/setup.bat

# User personalization (Soniox context terms etc.)
# Template: personal_settings.example.json (committed)
personal_settings.json

# Claude Code local-only notes (personal/session-specific; CLAUDE.md is committed)
CLAUDE.local.md